{"version":3,"term":{"cols":90,"rows":24},"timestamp":1783436224,"command":"omegaflow recording=quickstart-demo step=session","title":"Quickstart Demo"}
[0.392, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Install the OmegaFlow CLI.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.269, "o", "Successfully installed omegaflow-0.2.0\r\n"]
[0.027, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.036, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Run bootstrap from your repository root.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.476, "o", "workspace recordings\r\ncreated .omegaflow/config.yaml\r\ncreated recordings/config.yaml\r\ncreated recordings/quickstart/index.md\r\ncreated recordings/quickstart/scripts/hello.sh\r\n\r\nnext    omegaflow recording=quickstart action=build\r\n"]
[0.208, "o", ".\r\n├── .omegaflow\r\n│   └── config.yaml\r\n└── recordings\r\n    ├── config.yaml\r\n    └── quickstart\r\n        ├── index.md\r\n        └── scripts\r\n            └── hello.sh\r\n"]
[0.220, "o", "---\r\nid: quickstart\r\ntitle: Quickstart\r\npublish:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  default: html\r\n  surfaces:\r\n    html:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      type: standalone_html\r\n      file: ${outputs.dir}/${id}.html\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "---\r\n\r\n# Quickstart\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nThis Markdown file is the source for one generated terminal video.\r\n\r\nThe YAML header names the recording, chooses output paths, and declares where\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "the finished video can be published. The prose explains the walkthrough for\r\nreaders and future maintainers. The fenced `studio-directive` blocks tell\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "OmegaFlow what to record.\r\n\r\n```yaml studio-directive\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "scene: Quickstart\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "```\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "The scene is the title shown by the player. Beats are the steps in the video.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "This beat runs a small shell script kept in this video's `scripts/` directory.\r\n\r\n```yaml studio-directive\r\nbeat:\r\n  id: hello\r\n  heading: Say Hello\r\n  narration: Run the support script and verify the terminal output.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  caption: A one-command terminal recording.\r\n  actions:\r\n  - commands:\r\n    - run_file: scripts/hello.sh\r\n      display: bash scripts/hello.sh\r\n      expect:\r\n        output_contains:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        - hello from quickstart\r\n```\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nPublish surfaces in the header let the same recording write a standalone HTML\r\npage. Add a docs surface when you want the build to update a documentation page.\r\n"]
[0.026, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.042, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Build the generated quickstart recording.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.964, "o", "pass wrote retimed cast: recordings/.omegaflow/videos/quickstart.retimed.cast\r\npass wrote publish surface: recordings/.omegaflow/videos/quickstart.html\r\n"]
[0.034, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.037, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Play the generated cast in the terminal.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
